Installation
============

1. Extract package with 'tar xzvf cmlfile-xxxx.tgz'

2. Type 'make lib'

3. Edit (if necessary) lines

	INSTDIR_INCLUDE = /usr/include
	INSTDIR_LIB = /usr/lib

   in 'makefile'
   
4. Become root and type 'make install'

5. Optional: 'make test' and run test routine with './test train.cml'



Uninstallation
==============

1. Become root and type 'make uninstall'

